миссар</i></span> у власти  ?][? if in_schleicher_majority_coalition_prussia: Большинство <span style="color: #BFC8CC;">**ФНЕГ**</span> ?][? if in_schleicher_right_coalition_prussia: Правая коалиция Шлейхера ?][? if not in_social_liberal_coalition_prussia and not in_social_catholic_coalition_prussia and not in_weimar_coalition_prussia and not in_grand_coalition_prussia and not in_far_right_coalition_prussia and not in_popular_front_prussia and not in_left_front_prussia and not in_center_right_coalition_prussia and not in_right_coalition_prussia and not spd_toleration_prussia and not prussia_leader == "Папен" and prussia_leader != "Шлейхер" and chancellor != nsdap_chancellor and ddp_name != 0: Переходное правительство ?]

